Package: CCNV
Title: Generating Cumulative Copy Number Variation Plots From DNA Methylation Data
Version: 0.0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Antonia", "Gocke", , "an.gocke@uke.de", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0009-0007-5828-6637‚‚")), person("Yannis", "Schumann", , "schumany@hsu-hh.de", role = c("aut"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2379-200X")))
Description: This package can read idats and infers the copy number data. It 
    then segments the data, either cumulatively or consecutively and can then 
    create cumulative copy number variation plots and the corresponding 
    frequency plots.
